<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Essence Beauty Studio</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff7f8;
            color: #3d2b2f;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7a8b8, #d9879b);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px 8%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 85vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(61, 43, 47, 0.45), rgba(61, 43, 47, 0.45)),
                        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516975080664-ed2fc6a32937?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80");
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 8%;
            color: white;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 650px;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #d9879b;
            padding: 15px 28px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #f7dce3;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        section {
            padding: 70px 8%;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 34px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #b85f78;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 45px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #6c555b;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .services {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(184, 95, 120, 0.15);
            text-align: center;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #b85f78;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #6c555b;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .about {
            background-color: #ffe7ed;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            align-items: center;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .about img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .about-text h2 {
            font-size: 34px;
            color: #b85f78;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-text p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #5c464c;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .benefits {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .benefit {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(184, 95, 120, 0.12);
        }

        .benefit span {
            font-size: 35px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .contact {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d9879b, #b85f78);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact h2 {
            font-size: 34px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .contact p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .contact .btn {
            margin-top: 25px;
            color: #b85f78;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #3d2b2f;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 22px;
        }

        .whatsapp-fixed {
            position: fixed;
            right: 22px;
            bottom: 22px;
            background-color: #25d366;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 18px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            z-index: 10;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                text-align: center;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            nav {
                margin-top: 18px;
            }

            nav a {
                display: inline-block;
                margin: 8px 10px;
            }

            .hero h2 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Essence Beauty Studio</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="#inicio">Início</a>
            <a href="#servicos">Serviços</a>
            <a href="#sobre">Sobre</a>
            <a href="#contato">Contato</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" id="inicio">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h2>Realce sua beleza com cuidado e delicadeza</h2>
            <p>Especialistas em depilação, design de sobrancelhas e cílios para valorizar ainda mais o seu olhar.</p>
            <a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/5500000000000" target="_blank">Agendar horário</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="servicos">
        <h2 class="section-title">Nossos Serviços</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Atendimentos feitos com carinho, higiene e atenção aos detalhes para você se sentir linda e confiante.</p>

        <div class="services">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Depilação</h3>
                <p>Depilação com técnica segura, ambiente higienizado e cuidado para deixar sua pele macia e bem tratada.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Sobrancelhas</h3>
                <p>Design de sobrancelhas personalizado para harmonizar o seu rosto e destacar sua beleza natural.</p>
            </div>

